Package org.gvsig.educa.portableview.swing.impl.editor.addlayer

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    DefaultPortableViewAddLayerComponent
    Default implementation of PortableViewAddLayerComponent Creates a panel with 3 sections: Data Explorer type: Data explorer type to use Data Explorer Parameters: Parameters to use for locate data sources Source list: Sources found in this explorer parameters User can selected the explorer to use and its parameters to locate sources for layers.
    StoreParametersCellEditor
    Store Parameters Table cell editor for DefaultPortableViewAddLayerComponent sources list Shows store parameter description (delegates on StoreParametersCellRenderer) and a button which shows a dialog ( StoreParametersEditor) to modify the values.
    StoreParametersCellRenderer
    Store Parameters Table cell renderer for DefaultPortableViewAddLayerComponent sources list Shows store parameter description.
    StoreParametersEditor
    Dialog to edit Data Store parameters (used by StoreParametersCellEditor) Uses DynObjectSwingManager to generate components
